# Once on a history entry, we can edit it as usual.
run
key left
key left
type woo
----
-- view:
[40m[37m> [0m[0m[40mpeter parker was not spidermwoo[0m[40m[7ma[0m[0m[40mn [0m[40m  [0m‚ê§
