[40m[37m> [0m[0m[40mthis is a big world indeed[0m[40m[7m [0m[0m[40m[0m[40m         [0m‚ê§
[90mM-?[0m [90mtoggle key help[0m[90m ‚Ä¢ [0m[90mC-d[0m [90merase/stop[0m[90m ‚Ä¢ [0m[90mC-c[0m [90mclear/cancel[0m[90m ‚Ä¢ [0m[90mC-r[0m [90msearch hist[0m[90m ‚Ä¢ [0m[90mM-.[0m [90mhide/show prompt[0müõá

# The changes to the history entry above are not preserved, because we
# didn't accept the input.
run
key alt+p
----
-- view:
[40m[37m> [0m[0m[40mpeter parker was not spiderman[0m[40m[7m [0m[0m[40m[0m[40m     [0m‚ê§
